  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Now!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1653692132\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>SudoKube is the first Sudoku game set on 3D cubes. Each level is formed by 6 sudoku puzzles that share the solution in the cube edges. Something unique and unprecedented!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>All sudoku rules are applied and the whole cube also has only one solution, so it's really intuitive for a regular sudoku player;<br></li><li>Practice every day and keep your brain sharp;<br></li><li><strong>Infinite 2x2 puzzles</strong>  if you just want to warm up your brain before work;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/0438f87d05bed33427c7c518107128db.poster.avif?t=1653692132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/0438f87d05bed33427c7c518107128db.webm?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/0438f87d05bed33427c7c518107128db.mp4?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Infinite easy 3x3 puzzles</strong> if you want to challenge yourself before your next meeting;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/537bb6bb57a21c7eb0f1942e93e42a47.poster.avif?t=1653692132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/537bb6bb57a21c7eb0f1942e93e42a47.webm?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/537bb6bb57a21c7eb0f1942e93e42a47.mp4?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Infinite hard 3x3 puzzles</strong> if you are a experienced Sudoku player and have enough time available;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/e49db4483cac2f562ad89b7588211cca.poster.avif?t=1653692132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/e49db4483cac2f562ad89b7588211cca.webm?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/e49db4483cac2f562ad89b7588211cca.mp4?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>A single souls-like 4x4 puzzle</strong> if you feel fearless and think that nothing can harm your brain! Do not try to start this level if you are not willing to spend hours facing a single puzzle. Risk of brain melting and severe damage to your self-esteem. You declare that you take full responsibility for your choice.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/28acf1c513f43f36206b0e6e69f62a7c.poster.avif?t=1653692132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/28acf1c513f43f36206b0e6e69f62a7c.webm?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/28acf1c513f43f36206b0e6e69f62a7c.mp4?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>           <i>Note: Generating this 4x4 puzzle is quite expensive for us. If 100 people complete this puzzle, they will enter a permanent in-game hall of fame, and we pledge to update the game with 5 more 4x4 puzzles when that happens.</i>",
  "about_the_game": "SudoKube is the first Sudoku game set on 3D cubes. Each level is formed by 6 sudoku puzzles that share the solution in the cube edges. Something unique and unprecedented!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>All sudoku rules are applied and the whole cube also has only one solution, so it's really intuitive for a regular sudoku player;<br></li><li>Practice every day and keep your brain sharp;<br></li><li><strong>Infinite 2x2 puzzles</strong>  if you just want to warm up your brain before work;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/0438f87d05bed33427c7c518107128db.poster.avif?t=1653692132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/0438f87d05bed33427c7c518107128db.webm?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/0438f87d05bed33427c7c518107128db.mp4?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Infinite easy 3x3 puzzles</strong> if you want to challenge yourself before your next meeting;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/537bb6bb57a21c7eb0f1942e93e42a47.poster.avif?t=1653692132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/537bb6bb57a21c7eb0f1942e93e42a47.webm?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/537bb6bb57a21c7eb0f1942e93e42a47.mp4?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>Infinite hard 3x3 puzzles</strong> if you are a experienced Sudoku player and have enough time available;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/e49db4483cac2f562ad89b7588211cca.poster.avif?t=1653692132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/e49db4483cac2f562ad89b7588211cca.webm?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/e49db4483cac2f562ad89b7588211cca.mp4?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>A single souls-like 4x4 puzzle</strong> if you feel fearless and think that nothing can harm your brain! Do not try to start this level if you are not willing to spend hours facing a single puzzle. Risk of brain melting and severe damage to your self-esteem. You declare that you take full responsibility for your choice.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/28acf1c513f43f36206b0e6e69f62a7c.poster.avif?t=1653692132\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/28acf1c513f43f36206b0e6e69f62a7c.webm?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770230/extras/28acf1c513f43f36206b0e6e69f62a7c.mp4?t=1653692132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>           <i>Note: Generating this 4x4 puzzle is quite expensive for us. If 100 people complete this puzzle, they will enter a permanent in-game hall of fame, and we pledge to update the game with 5 more 4x4 puzzles when that happens.</i>",
